# Auto-Run Operators with Lambda-Operators Integration

Auto-run configuration for Controlled Rupture Operator sequences, integrated with Lambda Engine mode awareness.

## When to Apply

Apply this rule when:
- Specific conditions detected (large files, errors, goals, etc.)
- Need automatic operator application
- Want operator-guided auto-responses
- Need context-aware operator triggers

